      <h1>Linxira OS Documentation</h1>
      <p>Welcome to the official Linxira OS documentation. This site covers only Linxira-specific features. For general Linux questions, refer to the <a href="https://wiki.archlinux.org/" target="_blank">Arch Wiki</a>.</p>

      <h2>Quick Navigation</h2>
      <a href="/en/docs/install/" class="doc-card"><h3>Installation Guide</h3><p>Download ISO, create bootable media, and complete installation.</p></a>
